{"tid":2492213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"親共派：如果判斷「唔好投白票」不是反話？","createTime":"2021-04-17T03:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T03:22:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7d7f3f31f2cf5b348865e3d7f3f3cc46091742","tid":2492213,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"鍾國斌稱立例禁煽惑投白票或有反效果 羅健熙指無謂<br />\n<br />\n政府提出完善選舉制度綜合修訂條例草案中，加入新罪行，任何人在選舉期間內藉公開活動，煽惑他人不投票、投白票或廢票，即屬非法，最高可判監3年。自由黨黨魁鍾國斌認為條文，可能帶出反效果，政府好心做壞事；民主黨主席羅健熙則形容有關條文是無謂。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌在本台節目《星期六問責》表示，相信當局訂立有關法例後，不會再有人鼓吹投白票，相信政府是擔心選舉或出現預期不到的情況，他說要相信市民自己的決定，立例可能會出現反效果。<br />\n<br />\n羅健熙就估計政府是純因為面子問題，擔心白票多，影響選舉認受性，但他說有關條文令市民強烈反感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586278-20210417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586278-20210417.htm&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=1bff8cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586278-20210417.htm&h=41668056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586278-20210417.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a71d85ea8672cfa0a69a2a869c7859842acd49f2","tid":2492213,"uid":88578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會發展到，一有人講「白票」兩個字，就犯國安法？"},{"pid":"fb93c1ad7851725ecc04e9693d63c147eb9cf615","tid":2492213,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"支那賓準備好成個党冚家剷未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d86ea7875fbde2f3c0113c58e552f6c3cde5a74","tid":2492213,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR6JAXrMxvYszkLwDWLTRMtqErVC7mcBduFcvsC9ABZ4o?filename=AtgMqZt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtgM